-
-```markdown
-# Product Requirements Document: [Project Name]
-
-## 1. Overview
-- **Problem Statement**: ...
-- **Product Vision**: ...
-- **Target Users**: ...
-- **Success Metrics**: ...
-
-## 2. Goals & Non-Goals
-### Goals
-- ...
-### Non-Goals (Explicitly Out of Scope)
-- ...
-
-## 3. User Personas
-- **[Persona Name]**: [description, needs, behaviors]
-
